Note: Outer-Let + inner-Set is the canonical Runa pattern for conditional value
Note: assignment. After block scoping was added, the outer slot must still be
Note: reachable from both branches and after End If.
Note: Expected exit code: 99

Process called "main" returns Integer:
    Let result be 0
    Let x be 5

    If x is greater than 0:
        Set result to 99
    Otherwise:
        Set result to 1
    End If

    Return result
End Process
